data.description: Welcome to 5800 Bindweed St. This beautifully maintained home features, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath, open concept layout with additional room for second family room, game room, library etc. Upgrades include Granite countertops in kitchen, new laminate natural wood flooring throughout the main living area, and primary bedroom, new roof and gutters, installed in 2021, stained shutters and wood fence, Covered patio, two car garage with rear access. This must-see property is Located in Primrose Crossing, seconds away from Chisolm Trail Parkway, and just minutes away from shopping and dining, READY FOR NEW OWNERS!
